    <script type="text/javascript">
        function LoginPage_OnLoad() {

            document.getElementById('screenResolution').value = "'" + screen.width + 'x' + screen.height + "'";

            //focus redirection
            var loginTextBox = window.document._all("LoginTextBox");
            var LoginPanel = window.document._all("LoginPanel");
            if (typeof (loginTextBox) != 'undefined' && loginTextBox != null) {
                LoginPanel.style.display = "";
                loginTextBox.focus();
            }
        }

        var key;

        function GetRandomSalt(callback) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "LoginPage.aspx/GetRandomSalt",
                data: "{}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                async: "true",
                success: function (randomSalt) {
                    callback(randomSalt.d);
                }
            });
        }

        function ValidateForm(sender) {
            try {
                if (!Page_ClientValidate()) {
                    window.focus();
                    return false;
                }

                sender.disabled = true;

                if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginSSOButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginSSOButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SaveButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("CancelButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(ChangePasswordCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("AskQuestions_SubmitQuestionsButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("AskQuestions_cancelQuestionsButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(AnswerSecurityQuestionsCallback);
            }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_BtnSubmit")) {
                    document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_btnCancel").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(SetupSecurityQuestionsCallback);
                }
            }
            finally {
                return false;        //ensure no postback
            }
        }

        function SwitchOffSsoValidation() {
            if (!/\S+/.test(window.document._all("LoginSSOTextBox").value) &&
                !/\S+/.test(window.document._all("PasswordSSOTextBox").value) &&
                /\S+/.test(window.document._all("NetworkSSOTextBox").value)) {
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("LoginSSOTextBoxValidator");
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("PasswordSSOTextBoxValidator");
            }
        }

        $(function () {
            if (T360.IsMSIE7OrLess()) {
                $(window).resize(function () { $('.Document').height($('.Document').parent().height()); });
                $(window).resize();
                $('.DisclaimerText').css('position', 'absolute');

            if ($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height()) {

                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height(0);
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height());

                $(window).resize();
            }
            if ($('td.tdCenter').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdCenter').offset().top) {
                $('div.accountAgreement').addClass('eqie10');
            }
        });

        require(['globalHeader', 'bookmarkManager', 'order!jquery', 'order!t360bookmarkTree', 'underscore'], function (header, bookmarkManager) {
            // Create our tree
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree').t360bookmarkTree({
                dataUrl: '/Bookmarks/GetBookmarks',
                loadDataOnCreate: false,
                onActivate: function(node) {
                    if (!node.data.isFolder) {
                        var url = node.data.url;
                        mainFrame.navigateToUrl(url);
                        header.hideAllPanels();
                        node.deactivate();
                    }
                }
            });

            // This will add our bookmark manager to the window object (YUCK! But needed so we can get to it from the legacy stuff).
            // It will also return us the bookmark manager to work with, so we don't have to get it off the window.
            var manager = bookmarkManager($('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree').data('t360bookmarkTree'), $('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree'));
            manager.rootFolderId = '206349';
            
            header.setOnLoadBookmarks(manager.loadTree);
            
            // Add our event handlers
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelAddBookmark').off('click.t360bookmarks');
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelAddBookmark').on('click.t360bookmarks', function () {
                if ($(this).hasClass('disabled')) return false;
                
                $.showDialog(manager.addBookmarkUrl, [manager.pageBookmarkName], {
                    width: 480, 
                    height: 300, 
                    title: 'Add Bookmark', 
                    callback: function(result) {
                        if (result == null || result === "") return;
                        
                        var results = result.split('');
                        if (results[0] === 'AddBookmark') {
                            $.post('/Bookmarks/AddLink', {
                                    folderId: results[2],
                                    title: results[1],
                                    url: manager.pageBookmarkUrl
                                }, function() {
                                    manager.reloadTree();
                                });
                        }
                    }
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        window.IsMainFrame = true;

        window.showCustomPrintMenu = function (links, target) {
            var dic = JsonFormatter.deserialize(links);
            var printMenu = $('#customPrintMenu');
            printMenu.empty();
            var ul = $("<ul>").appendTo(printMenu);
            for (var link in dic) {
                var li = $("<li>").css("display", "block").appendTo(ul);
                var ahref = $("<a>" + link.toString() + "</a>").attr("href", "javascript:void(0)").appendTo(li);
                var func = new Function('return this.' + dic[link]);
                var proxyFunc = $.proxy(func, target);
                ahref.on('click', proxyFunc);
            }
            printMenu.show();
            if (window.event.stopPropagation) {
                window.event.stopPropagation();
            } else {
                window.event.cancelBubble = true;
            }
        };

        window.sysToolbarInit = function (contentFrame) {
            var setupButton = function (name, funcs, uniqueId) {
                var button = $("#" + uniqueId);
                button.off('click');
                if (typeof funcs[name] === 'function') {
                    var proxyFunc = $.proxy(funcs[name], contentFrame);
                    button.on('click', proxyFunc);
                    button.show();
                } else {
                    button.hide();
                }
            };

            var contentFrameSupportsButtons = contentFrame != null && contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs != null;
            var funcs = contentFrameSupportsButtons ? contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs : [];

            setupButton('print', funcs, 'sysToolbarPrint');
            setupButton('email', funcs, 'sysToolbarEmail');
        };

      
        function getCountOfTabs() {
            var key = getTabCountKey();

            if (window.localStorage[key] == undefined) {
                window.localStorage[key] = 0;
            }

            return parseInt(window.localStorage[key]);
        }

        function setCountOfTabs(val) {        
            window.localStorage[getTabCountKey()] = val;
        }

        $(document).first().ready(function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {

                if (!window.sessionStorage.isLogged) {
                            
                    if (getCountOfTabs() > 0) {                    
                        window.sessionStorage.isLogged = true;
                    } else {                        
                        toolBar.logOff();
                    }
                }

                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() + 1);            
            }
        });

        $(window).first().one("beforeunload", function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {
                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() - 1);
            }
        });

	function initWelcomePerspective()
	{
		if (WS.customPerspective != null) {
			// Custom Perspective mode
			switchToPerspective(WS.customPerspective);
			// Reset the value
			WS.customPerspective = null;
		}
		else {
			switchToPerspective("welcome", true)
		}
	}
	
	function reloadDocStructureAfterSaveAs(strEntry)
	{
		wt();
		DS.isNew = false;
		DS.isSaveAction= true;
		//Update the viewType
		if (isPDF)
			WS.strViewType = "P";
		else if (isInteractive)
			WS.strViewType = "I";
		else
			WS.strViewType = "H";        
        
		var url = "ajaxInitDocument" + _appExt + "?getAjax=true&iViewerID=" + WS.iViewerID + "&sEntry=" + strEntry+"&appKind="+WS.appKind;
		ajaxUpdater({
			"url": url,
			"postCB": updatePerspective,
			"ajaxErrorCB": manageAjaxError
		});	
	}
	
	function initPerspective(docId, containerId)
	{
		strDocID=docId;
		if (DS.containerID != containerId)
		{
			//Check if has customization folder
			if (WS._customization != null && WS._customization.enabled && WS._customization.hasCustoFolder && parent.goReloadViewer != null)
			{
				_askConfirmationBeforeClosingDoc = false;
				parent.goReloadViewer(docId, containerId, _root);
				return;
			}
			DS.containerID = containerId;
		}
		
		var initDocUrl = "ajaxInitDocument" + _appExt
	initDocUrl += "?getAjax=true&iViewerID=" + WS.iViewerID +"&appKind="+WS.appKind +"&id=" + docId +"&pvl="+WS.pvl;

		WS.strViewType = (WS.strViewType == "")?"H":WS.strViewType // set default view mode to reading if no param
			
		ajaxUpdater({
			"url": initDocUrl,
			"postCB": updatePerspective,
			"ajaxErrorCB": manageAjaxError
		});		
	}

	//called by query panel	
	function initPerspectiveFromToken(strEntry, isNewDoc, viewType)
	{
		wt();
		
		var initDocUrl = "ajaxInitDocument" + _appExt
		initDocUrl += "?getAjax=true&iViewerID=" + WS.iViewerID + "&sEntry=" + strEntry;

		WS.strViewType = (viewType != null)?viewType:"I"; 

		if(isNewDoc) //force left panel
		{
			WS._showLeftPane=_paneState.normal;
			WS._leftPaneSel= "resultObj"; 
		}		

		ajaxUpdater({
			"url": initDocUrl,
			"postCB": updatePerspective,
			"ajaxErrorCB": manageAjaxError
		});		
	}	
	
	function updatePerspective(obj)
	{	
		if (obj) {
			
			// DS : document settings ( prefs, secu) document dependant
			if (window.DS)
			{
				obj.isNew = window.DS.isNew;
				var isSaveAction = typeof(window.DS.isSaveAction) != "undefined" ?  window.DS.isSaveAction : false;
				obj.isSaveAction = isSaveAction;
			}

			//update default doc Name
			if(obj.strDocName =="")
			{
				obj.strDocName = _defaultDocName;
				obj.isNew=true;
			}
			
			window.DS = obj;
				
			// clean tokens
			resetStatesCB()
			
			checkPerspectiveVars()
			
			setDictionary(null); 
			
			//Apply customization before selecting perspective
			if (typeof(apply_customization_feature_behavior) != "undefined") {
				apply_customization_feature_behavior("viewdocument");	
			}
			
			if (WS.customPerspective != null) {
				// Custom Perspective mode
				switchToPerspective(WS.customPerspective);
				// Reset the value
				WS.customPerspective = null;
			}
			else if (WS.strViewType == "H") {
				// Static HTML
				switchToPerspective("view")
			}
			else if (WS.strViewType == "I") {
				switchToDesignPerspective();
			}
			else {
				// PDF Mode
				switchToPerspective("pdfView")
			}
			
			// strDocID is the new ID of selected/created document  
			if (typeof(strDocID) != "undefined")
			{
				// notify doc ID change
				eventManager.notify(_EVT_DOCID_UPDATE);	
			}
		}
	}
	
	function switchToDesignPerspective(setFocusOnTopLeftButton)
	{
		setFocusOnTopLeftButton = (setFocusOnTopLeftButton != null)?setFocusOnTopLeftButton:false;
		if (DS.designModeState == "structure") {
			// Force the design mode to structure
			switchToPerspective("structure", setFocusOnTopLeftButton);
		}
		else {
			// Interactive mode
			switchToPerspective("interactive", setFocusOnTopLeftButton);
		}
	}
	
	function checkPerspectiveVars()
	{

		var isHyperlinkDoc =isHyperlink();
 		if (!isHyperlinkDoc){

			setDocTitle(newDocName)		
		}else{
			setDocTitle(getHyperlinkTitle());		
		}
	    
		strDocName = DS.strDocName // used in getPDFView.jsp
		
		_showDrillBar = DS.arrReports[getReportIdxFromId(DS.iReportID)].drillBar;
			
		// TODO : check this	
		//if (DS.strDateFormat == "") strDateFormat=DS._localeDateFormat;
	
		strLastRefreshDate="";
		if ((DS.strLastRefreshDate == "") && (DS._lLastRefreshMilliSecDate!=0) )
		{
			dtDate=new Date(DS._lLastRefreshMilliSecDate);	
			strLastRefreshDate = formatDate(dtDate,strDateFormat);
		}
		if (strLastRefreshDate == "") strLastRefreshDate=_noRefreshYet; 
		if(DS.HanaOnlineMode) strLastRefreshDate="";
		
		// Display Creation date
				
		if ((DS.strCreationDate == "") && (DS.lCreationMilliSecTime != 0) )
		{
			strCreationDate=formatDate(new Date(DS.lCreationMilliSecTime),strDateFormat);
		}
	
		// Viewer properties
		
		//TODO: deprecated
		//blnNeedAnswerCP=<=blnNeedAnswerCP%>;
		blnNeedAnswerCP=false;
		
		var isOpenDocWithPrompts=(WS.isOpenDocWithPrompts)?WS.isOpenDocWithPrompts:false;
		if (isOpenDocWithPrompts)
		{
			// DHTML client will apply prompt parameters and refresh document too. So we must not refresh it again.
			doRefreshOnOpen = false;
		}
		else
		{
			// doRefreshOnOpen is set to true the document is Refresh On Open Or receive a parameter sRefresh=Y
			doRefreshOnOpen = DS.doRefreshOnOpen;
		}
		var isSaveAction = typeof(DS.isSaveAction) != "undefined" ?  DS.isSaveAction : false;
		
		//Incident 40318 / 2017 / [4.2 SP03] patch 5 SAVE AS results times out after 4.2 Upg
		// case of doc with refresh on Open and save as doc and drillbar activated

// 				DS.isSaveAction = false;
// 			// Send Refresh On Open document event
// 			eventManager.notify(_EVT_REFRESH_ON_OPEN);
// 		}
        if (doRefreshOnOpen)
        {
               if (isSaveAction) {
                      DS.doRefreshOnOpen = false;
                      doRefreshOnOpen = DS.doRefreshOnOpen;
               }
               else {
                      if (typeof(DS.isSaveAction) != "undefined")
                             DS.isSaveAction = false;
                      // Send Refresh On Open document event
                      eventManager.notify(_EVT_REFRESH_ON_OPEN);
               }
        }

		
		// TODO	 : deal with this
